#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.DIGGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.DIGGER"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Walks on solid ground, climbs walls, and walks upside-down on ceilings, transitioning freely around corners between all four surfaces. Can also burrow into soft natural tiles and tunnel through solid material, emerging back onto any surface. Cannot dig through very hard materials or refined metals."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.DUPLICANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.DUPLICANT"
msgid "Is 1 wide by 2 tall. Walks on solid ground and can travel vertically or horizontally on ladders. Can climb ledges up to 2 tiles tall, jump over gaps 1 tile wide, and drop down ledges up to 2 tiles tall. Can also reach a platform 2 tiles away horizontally and 1 tile up, or 1 tile away and 2 tiles up. Falls through larger drops, though will attempt to avoid this."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLOATER
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLOATER"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Hovers 1 tile above the nearest solid surface or liquid below it, following the terrain contour from above. If submerged by rising liquid, can swim to escape."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLYER_1X1
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLYER_1X1"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Flies freely through open air in any direction. If submerged by rising liquid, can swim to escape."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLYER_1X2
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLYER_1X2"
msgid "Occupies 1 wide by 2 tall. Flies freely through open air in any direction. If submerged by rising liquid, can swim to escape. Needs more vertical clearance than smaller flyers."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLYER_2X2
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.FLYER_2X2"
msgid "Occupies 2 wide by 2 tall. Flies freely through open air in any direction. If submerged by rising liquid, can swim to escape. Needs significant clearance to navigate."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.ROBOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.ROBOT"
msgid "Is 1 wide by 2 tall. Walks on solid ground and can travel vertically or horizontally on ladders. Can climb ledges up to 2 tiles tall, jump over gaps 1 tile wide, and drop down ledges up to 2 tiles tall. Can also reach a platform 2 tiles away horizontally and 1 tile up, or 1 tile away and 2 tiles up. Cannot use transit tubes or fire poles."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.ROBOT_FLYER
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.ROBOT_FLYER"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Flies freely through open air in any direction. Can pass through doors. If submerged by rising liquid, can swim to escape."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SURFACE_CLIMBER
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SURFACE_CLIMBER"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Walks on solid ground, climbs walls, and walks upside-down on ceilings, transitioning freely around corners between all four surfaces. On the floor, can climb ledges up to 2 tiles tall, cross gaps 1 tile wide, and reach platforms up to 2 tiles away horizontally and 2 tiles up."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SURFACE_CLIMBER_BABY
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SURFACE_CLIMBER_BABY"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Walks on solid ground, climbs walls, and walks upside-down on ceilings, transitioning freely around corners between all four surfaces. Cannot climb ledges, jump gaps, or cross drops on the floor, unlike an adult."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SWIMMER_1X1
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SWIMMER_1X1"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Swims through liquid in any direction. On dry land, flops around searching for nearby liquid but cannot walk."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SWIMMER_2X2
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.SWIMMER_2X2"
msgid "Occupies 2 wide by 2 tall. Swims through liquid in any direction. On dry land, flops around searching for nearby liquid but cannot walk. Needs more space to navigate than smaller swimmers."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.TREE_CLIMBER
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.TREE_CLIMBER"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Walks on solid ground, climbs walls, and walks upside-down on ceilings, transitioning freely around corners between all four surfaces. On the floor, can climb ledges up to 2 tiles tall, cross gaps 1 tile wide, and drop down ledges up to 2 tiles tall."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_1X1
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_1X1"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Walks on solid ground. Can climb ledges up to 2 tiles tall, cross gaps 1 tile wide, and drop down ledges up to 2 tiles tall."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_1X2
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_1X2"
msgid "Occupies 1 wide by 2 tall. Walks on solid ground. Can climb ledges up to 2 tiles tall, cross gaps 1 tile wide, and drop down ledges up to 2 tiles tall. Needs more vertical clearance than smaller walkers due to its height."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_2X2
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_2X2"
msgid "Occupies 2 wide by 2 tall. Walks on solid ground. Can climb or descend 1-tile ledges over a 2-tile horizontal distance, but cannot climb steeper ledges. Needs more clearance than smaller creatures due to its size."
msgstr ""

#. STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_BABY
msgctxt "STRINGS.ONIACCESS.DETAILS.PATHING_DESC.WALKER_BABY"
msgid "Occupies 1 tile. Walks on solid ground but can only move horizontally on flat surfaces. Cannot climb, jump, or cross gaps, unlike an adult."
msgstr ""

